8
00:00:19,152 --> 00:00:23,052
Ponsel itu ditemukan di bawah bangku yang ada di taman.

9
00:00:23,052 --> 00:00:24,852
Saat Ayumi pergi mengantarkan ponselnya...

10
00:00:29,552 --> 00:00:33,352
Aku tidak akan memaafkanmu lagi!

11
00:00:33,352 --> 00:00:34,752
Aku akan membunuhmu!

12
00:00:34,752 --> 00:00:37,552
Hei, Sumika.

13
00:00:37,552 --> 00:00:39,252
Tenanglah.

14
00:00:39,252 --> 00:00:41,252
Sumika.

15
00:00:44,552 --> 00:00:46,852
Matilah kau!

16
00:00:49,152 --> 00:00:51,552
